description: The Comic Book Digest gives you 80 pages of eight-page sample previews from 10 future comic titles from publishers like Image, Dreamwave, DBPro, and Arcana Studios. Read comics before you buy them! On the flip-side, join in the suspense as Agent Goodwin tracks down a serial killer in the exclusive full-length third issue release of Mike S. Miller's "Deal With The Devil" Articles and interviews from writers, publishers, and artists throughout the industry provide an inside look that benefit both the avid collector and the casual comic hobbyist.
